<h1 class="font-outfit text-2xl font-bold text-white border-b border-slate-700 pb-3 mb-6 mt-0">CONSUMABLES</h1>
<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Consumables are loot that can only be used once. You can hold up to five of each consumable at a time. Using a consumable doesnâ€™t require a roll unless required by the GM or the demands of the fiction.</p>
<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">To generate a random consumable, choose a rarity, roll the designated dice, and match the total to the item in the table:</p>
<ul class="text-slate-300 list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
<li class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white font-semibold">Common:</strong> 1d12 or 2d12</li>
<li class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white font-semibold">Uncommon:</strong> 2d12 or 3d12</li>
<li class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white font-semibold">Rare:</strong> 3d12 or 4d12</li>
<li class="leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white font-semibold">Legendary:</strong> 4d12 or 5d12</li>
</ul>
